<td align="left"><div class="blogPost column first"><h3>Iperius Backup 7.6.2</h3><p class="postHeader">06/05/2022</p><div class="column large"><h5 style="margin-top:15px; color:#666666;">New features</h5><ul class="list tick"><li>New options for <u>incremental replication of VMware ESXi virtual machines</u>: now you can choose between forever-full, <strong>forever-incremental</strong> modes or decide whether to redo a full after a certain number of incrementals. Don't forget that Iperius is able to make <strong>incremental replication from host to host even with ESXi Free</strong>.
</li>
<li>
Hyper-V backup now also supports virtual machine names with unicode characters (example: Chinese)
</li>
<li>
Several improvements and optimizations
</li>
</ul></div><div class="column large"><h5 style="margin-top:15px; color:#666666;">Fixed bugs</h5><ul class="list tick"><li>
Backup to Dropbox: fixed an issue due to authentication token expiration, due to Dropbox policy change on token life. Now Iperius requires the authentication method with client id and client secret, taken from the Dropbox app configuration.
</li>
<li>
Solved a problem of double start at logon (double icon in the tray) of Iperius Backup on Windows 11 systems
</li>
<li>
Some minor bugs fixed</li>
</ul></div><br /><br /><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.iperiusbackup.com/dsib.aspx">Free Download</a></div></td>
