</li>
<li>
It is now possible to set up <strong>automatic renewal </strong> by credit card for all licenses with an annual fee
</li>
</ul></div><div class="column large"><h5 style="margin-top:15px; color:#666666;">Fixed bugs</h5><ul class="list tick"><li>
