</tr><tr bgcolor=""><td align="left" style="display:none;">171</td>
<td align="left"><div class="blogPost column"><h3>Iperius Backup 7.5.5</h3><p class="postHeader">17/12/2021</p><div class="column large"><h5 style="margin-top:15px; color:#666666;">New features</h5><ul class="list tick"><li>Iperius Drive Image: added the option "keep partition tables", which allows you to create a disk image with the exact partition structure of the original disk
