</li>
</ul></div><div class="column large"><h5 style="margin-top:15px; color:#666666;">Fixed bugs</h5><ul class="list tick"><li>
Exchange Backup: Fixed Exchange backup engine run error on systems that have FIPS security mode enabled
</li>
<li>
Recovery drive creation: fixed a problem checking the removable drive
</li>
<li>
Hyper-V backup: fixed an error in the backup configuration in the case of virtual machines with special characters in the name
</li>
<li>
Some minor bugs fixed</li>
</ul></div></div></td>
